'''Candi''' chhai [[Yin-nì]] he hìn-yùng yit-chho ló-kú [[meu-é]], thai-phu-fun chhiùng [[Yin-thu-fu̍t-kau Sṳ̀-thoi]] pûn ngìn kien-li̍p ke.

Chhai yá-phién, sin-thù chhùng-pai [[Fu̍]] fe̍t-chá [[Yin-thu-kau]] ke [[sṳ̀n-mìn]].

Candi, yá-chak ki-fa m̀-tân-chhiang pâu-hàm meu-é ke yi-sṳ, me voi hìn-yùng phe̍t-chak ló-kú ke Yin-thu-fu̍t-kau Sṳ̀-thoi ke kien-chuk； kiûng-thien (''kraton''), yo̍k-thòng (''petirtaan''), mùn (''gapura'') tén-tén.
